content: Great game
The game doesn't work anymore. The tiles don't move properly. This used to be my favorite game.
I've had it for maybe a month and now it won't open for me anymore
Is a classic Mexican train dominos. Better than the others I have tried and you can change the names, which can be fun
Used to be one of my favorite games. Now half the time it doesn't even let me move a tile. Still a good game if you can get it to function.

Love this version of MTD, because it shows you the best train possible. You always have the option to do otherwise without the game telling you what you must do. It has some different rules from other versions, but it just adds to the charm of this MTD. Load it. Try it. Have fun.
If I could give a negative 5 I would need to refund back my money this game is horrible
Worth paying for this app. Love it.
Great game! Closest to the real thing that I've found. Good options, so you can play by the rules you are used to.
Fun, easy, great game to kill time in waiting rooms, etc.
Really well made app
Time passes quickly when playing.
Very nice version of the real game...really enjoyable!

Too many crashes, unfortunately. I had a galaxy s8+ and the game crashed all of the time. I have upgraded to a Note 10+, but still having the same issues. It is good when it works, but unfortunately I often cannot even open the app even after reinstalling and rebooting.
Very Buggy.. the game kept closing on it's own or restarting.
By far, this is the best and easiest to use version for the classic game: Pleasant design, nice features, intuitive interface.
I've been playing it for years and it's a great game, works very well. No problems at all.
This would be at least 4 stars except that after a week of playing I'm now unable to pick up and move tiles, making the game unplayable, not ok for a game I paid for.
replyContent: Remove the game from memory, and then restart. When you restart, you should see the screen that says "Loading...". Then it should be fine. Please let me know if that did not work, and I will help. scott@amuseware.com

First time app player,wasn't sure what to expaect
Very entertaining
Great fun!
i enjoy it. i wish it had options for different rules but its solid.
Screen layout / user interface is unclear, and you realize how it could use major improvements once you figure it out.
this is a very good game. I enjoy having it on my phone cause I like the game.
Great game!!
really fun
I really like this game. It's a tad different than the Mexican train I'm used to, but easy enough to adapt, and actually more enjoyable. Great job, thanks!
a lot of fun
Best graphics and play for Mexican Train!
Best Mexican Train app! Worth the minimal cost. I am addicted.

My husband and I are huge fans of Mexican Train and tried several apps before finding the app by Amuseware. We find this app to be the closest to playing in person. Very enjoyable. Bonus is that developer is very open to suggestions and fixes, as needed. We play this app almost every evening!
I love this version of Mexican Train. It is easy and fun to play on a small screen. I have loved the Windows version for years!

Fantastic Game! This is an update to an earlier version that stopped working with the last Android OS update. Loved the last one. This one's even better. Sleek, crisp, clean interface that runs smoothly. Lots of options. One of my favorite games next to the Triple Yatzy by the same developer. I'd definitely recommend most anything from him. They all seem to be hits in my book.

This is the best version of Mexican train dominoes out there. Mexican train dominoes is my favorite game and have tried other versions in my opinion there is no better version than this try it I promise you you will not be disappointed!!
Fun, somewhat addictive, and SO much better than the competition!
This is a great game.
recently updated game to deal with Android induced issues. excellent game, lots of options. i love it.
I have several Dominoes apps and this is by far the best. It has so many options allowing you to choose from a variety of ways to play the game. It's very reasonably priced and there are no ads!!!
BEST MEXICAN TRAIN DOMINOES EVER!
